show.description: Josline was raised in warmth by stepparents who loved her as their own. Her life shatters when she learns her real parents—powerful and ruthless elites—want her back. Trapped in a world of secrets and cruelty, Josline dies… only to return with one goal: uncover the truth and rewrite her fate.
